{"tid":2039860,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[民族自強] 有無熟悉香港本土音樂既巴絲可以喺twitter開個台推廣本土音樂","createTime":"2020-05-28T08:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T20:43:57.000Z","uid":344912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d00e041edea0253ef2baa53b667ede11da029927","tid":2039860,"uid":344912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T08:37:25.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n小妹整緊個文宣想叫人支持twitter戰線<br />\n入面想叫人順便follow自己鍾意既本地歌手<br />\n但係我搵 #香港音樂 好似無咩大路既result<br />\n有無有心巴絲可以去果邊推廣下<br />\n因為twitter好多日本人/歐美人用<br />\n其實係復興香港文化既好平台<br />\n我都唔想以後識親啲外國人仲係同我講<br />\n&lsquo;bruce Lee？jacky chan?'<br />\n係時候推廣啲香港文化出去！！<br />\n同埋比自己人！！<br />\n<br />\nerr.. <br />\n如果有人做既我會好感激<br />\n認同麻煩推一下<br />\n[p牌的悲哀]<br />\n如果今日內無人做既我應該會自己做<br />\n因為想出埋twitter戰線教學先<br />\nthanks!!!"},{"pid":"5455ef0dcab6fa9ff875b8546937580bf528e98c","tid":2039860,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"試下search廣東歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我搵到有人貼歌詞<br />\n有人貼樂評blog link"},{"pid":"9862e936dbfc535fdbdd08cbf02e77b2ff480e57","tid":2039860,"uid":88300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"好似幾好!  <br />\n有種&quot;昔日香港&quot;feel"},{"pid":"5771d281979b0894f06279bce01e7e10f2834311","tid":2039860,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:11:47.000Z","msg":"劉明跟進"},{"pid":"62e73382596e956f004ee594681f197054f70eec","tid":2039860,"uid":247799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"我一直都有呢個諗法 但唔知用咩方法去promote廣東歌俾人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7a2ef17b9d7f1244081f0a9b282e0df810d4ea","tid":2039860,"uid":219334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"非常支持！一向覺得軟文化係民族實力最重要一環之一。要光復香港，先光復香港文化。但我都唔多熟twitter, 具體可以點做？"},{"pid":"842098c058f5a76bf1555bd34ed9818e96d4cd4d"